Interface SecuredAlt

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Alt, Container, FrontsNode, RDFNode, Resource, SecuredContainer, SecuredItem, SecuredRDFNode, SecuredResource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SecuredAltImpl

    public interface SecuredAlt
extends Alt, SecuredContainer
    The interface for secured Alt instances. Use the SecuredAlt.Factory to create instances
